Alright, last question.

00:37:22.630 --> 00:37:23.503
Go. I'll be-- You'll be
quick and I'll be quick.

00:37:24.890 --> 00:37:24.956
&gt;&gt; Okay. Scott, can you tell us
about how the effects of the economy

00:37:29.290 --> 00:37:29.596
and recession have had on the legal
profession, changes in compensation

00:37:33.650 --> 00:37:34.496
from billable hours to
flat rate [laughter]?

00:37:35.670 --> 00:37:39.003
How does that change how
you depict your characters

00:37:41.480 --> 00:37:44.746
so for the 20 years you've
been writing about law?

00:37:45.860 --> 00:37:49.793
&gt;&gt; You know, I don't know yet
because I haven't had a chance

00:37:52.640 --> 00:37:53.276
to write about the
contemporary legal environment.

00:37:55.270 --> 00:37:59.536
There's a little bit of reference
to it and in Innocent where one

00:37:59.750 --> 00:38:00.363
of the characters is working as
an associate in big law firms says

00:38:03.470 --> 00:38:03.826
that she suddenly sees her
future as being, you know,

00:38:06.580 --> 00:38:06.813
one where she was gonna get
all her litigation experience

00:38:10.080 --> 00:38:11.413
in bankruptcy court.

00:38:13.080 --> 00:38:14.080


00:38:14.250 --> 00:38:18.316
Lawyers in a strata have had it
very, very good in this county

00:38:20.620 --> 00:38:25.086
for several decades and you know,
it's hard at this point to believe

00:38:30.090 --> 00:38:33.356
that it's ever gonna quite
go back to what it was.

00:38:35.010 --> 00:38:39.276
Those kinds of predictions though
inevitably end up proving false

00:38:39.480 --> 00:38:41.213
but I know a lot of people

00:38:41.480 --> 00:38:45.680
in the profession don't quite see
it coming back in the same way

00:38:46.130 --> 00:38:48.796
but I will say to you
what was said to me

00:38:49.340 --> 00:38:51.540
when I began the practice of law.

00:38:52.290 --> 00:38:54.823
Clients will always
find a good lawyer.

00:38:55.480 --> 00:38:56.946
It will always happen.

00:38:57.480 --> 00:39:01.346
One of the great, great things
about the practice of law is

00:39:01.420 --> 00:39:04.953
that in its own way, it's
extraordinarily meritocratic

00:39:05.700 --> 00:39:09.100
and good lawyers who work
hard and who are dedicated

00:39:09.380 --> 00:39:12.780
to their clients tend to
be rewarded in that system.

